Continuous
Once per turn, if a face-up "Crystal Beast" monster(s) you control is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can Special Summon 1 "Crystal Beast" monster from your Deck. If this card is face-up in your Spell & Trap Zone: You can send it to the Graveyard, then target 1 "Crystal Beast" card you control and 1 other card on the field; return them to the hand. This card's effects cannot be activated in the same chain.
